    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels less firm than it used to. Cosmetically, there are several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some interior upholstery wear that reflect its regular use. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its former glory or for someone needing an affordable, functional daily driver.",
      "price": 21500.0,
