      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Essential preventive maintenance is complete, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural integrity. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that provides excellent power delivery through the corners. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a recently updated cooling system. A purist\u2019s spec focused on performance and mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 32500.0,
